{"id":"lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0001","text":"你叫我這麼感動 但是這是我 你有可能戲弄","structure":{"line_index":1,"char_count":18},"semantics":{"themes":["情感的困惑","懷疑與試探"],"sentiment":"NEUTRAL","keywords":["感動","戲弄","可能"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[5,4,5,5,3,9,2,2,2,5,2,5,5,5,9,0,4,2],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["nei5","giu3","ngo5","ze5","mo1","gam2","dung6","daan6","si6","ze5","si6","ngo5","nei5","jau5","ho2","nang4","hei3","lung6"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"叫","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"這麼","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"感動","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"但是","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"這","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"是","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"有","pos":"AUX"},{"text":"可能","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"戲弄","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"以疑問句開頭，表達對對方情感的困惑與試探，語氣帶有不確定。"},"source":{"title":"夢到內河","artists":["張國榮"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1093","prev_line_id":null,"next_line_id":"lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0002","paragraph_id":"para_01"}}
{"id":"lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0002","text":"怎麼肯親手展示 如何被抱擁 我兩手還有用","structure":{"line_index":2,"char_count":18},"semantics":{"themes":["自我懷疑","情感的距離"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["親手","展示","抱擁","兩手","有用"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[9,3,9,3,9,9,2,0,0,2,5,9,5,5,9,0,5,2],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["zam2","mo1","hang2","can1","sau2","zin2","si6","jyu4","ho4","bei6","pou5","jung2","ngo5","loeng5","sau2","waan4","jau5","jung6"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"怎麼","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"肯","pos":"AUX"},{"text":"親手","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"展示","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"如何","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"被","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"抱","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"擁","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"兩手","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"還有","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"用","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"使用反問句，質疑對方展示親密的方式，並反思自己的存在價值，語氣帶有失落。"},"source":{"title":"夢到內河","artists":["張國榮"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1093","prev_line_id":"lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0001","next_line_id":"lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0003","paragraph_id":"para_01"}}
{"id":"lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0003","text":"你贈我一巴掌吧 爲什麼未痛 我也許在發夢","structure":{"line_index":3,"char_count":18},"semantics":{"themes":["情感的試探","自我麻痺"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["一巴掌","未痛","發夢"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[5,2,5,3,3,9,2,2,3,2,4,5,5,9,2,4,2],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["nei5","zang6","ngo5","jat1","baa1","zoeng2","baa6","sam6","mo1","mei6","tung3","ngo5","jaa5","heoi2","zoi6","faat3","mung6"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"贈","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"一巴掌","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"吧","pos":"PART"},{"text":"爲什麼","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"未痛","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"也許","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"在","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"發夢","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"提出極端的請求，並質疑疼痛的真實性，暗示可能處於夢境或自我欺騙中，語氣帶有痛苦與迷茫。"},"source":{"title":"夢到內河","artists":["張國榮"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1093","prev_line_id":"lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0002","next_line_id":"lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0004","paragraph_id":"para_01"}}
{"id":"lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0004","text":"當初的溫馨舉動 拿來做分手的慶功 令我筋竭力窮","structure":{"line_index":4,"char_count":21},"semantics":{"themes":["分手","疲憊","失落"],"sentiment":"VERY_NEGATIVE","keywords":["溫馨","舉動","分手","慶功","筋竭力窮"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[3,3,3,3,9,2,0,0,2,3,9,3,4,3,2,5,3,4,2,0],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["co1","dik1","wan1","hing1","geoi2","dung6","naa4","loi4","zou6","fan1","sau2","dik1","hing3","gung1","ling6","ngo5","gan1","kit3","lik6","kung4"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"當初","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"的","pos":"PART"},{"text":"溫馨","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"舉動","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"拿來","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"做","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"分手","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"的","pos":"PART"},{"text":"慶功","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"令","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"筋","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"竭力","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"窮","pos":"ADJ"}],"syntax_notes":"將過去的溫馨與現在的分手對比，諷刺地稱為「慶功」，表達極度的疲憊與失落感。"},"source":{"title":"夢到內河","artists":["張國榮"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1093","prev_line_id":"lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0003","next_line_id":"lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0005","paragraph_id":"para_01"}}
{"id":"lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0005","text":"自那日遺下我 我早化做磷火 湖泊上伴你這天鵝","structure":{"line_index":5,"char_count":20},"semantics":{"themes":["被遺棄","轉化","痛苦的陪伴"],"sentiment":"VERY_NEGATIVE","keywords":["遺下","化做","磷火","湖泊","天鵝"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[2,5,2,0,2,5,5,9,4,2,0,9,0,2,2,5,5,3,0],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["zi6","naa5","jat6","wai4","haa6","ngo5","ngo5","zou2","faa3","zou6","leon4","fo2","wu4","bok6","bun6","nei5","ze5","tin1","ngo4"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"自","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"那日","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"遺下","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"早","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"化做","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"磷火","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"湖泊","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"上伴","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"這","pos":"DET"},{"text":"天鵝","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"描述被遺棄後，自身經歷痛苦的轉化，以「磷火」比喻，並在湖泊上「伴」著對方，語氣充滿悲傷與無奈。"},"source":{"title":"夢到內河","artists":["張國榮"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1093","prev_line_id":"lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0004","next_line_id":"lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0006","paragraph_id":"para_02"}}
{"id":"lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0006","text":"但你爲何還要 也許單手 怕扼不死我","structure":{"line_index":6,"char_count":15},"semantics":{"themes":["殘酷的對待","恐懼","求死"],"sentiment":"VERY_NEGATIVE","keywords":["爲何","還要","單手","扼不死"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[2,5,0,0,4,5,9,3,9,4,3,3,9,5],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["daan6","nei5","ho4","waan4","jiu3","jaa5","heoi2","daan1","sau2","paa3","ak1","bat1","sei2","ngo5"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"但","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"爲何","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"還要","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"也許","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"單手","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"怕","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"扼","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"不","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"死","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"}],"syntax_notes":"再次質疑對方的行為，並表達害怕對方無法徹底傷害自己，語氣帶有恐懼與絕望。"},"source":{"title":"夢到內河","artists":["張國榮"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1093","prev_line_id":"lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0005","next_line_id":"lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0007","paragraph_id":"para_02"}}
{"id":"lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0007","text":"若要死 這一刻正是 愉快 高峯 請給我更多","structure":{"line_index":7,"char_count":17},"semantics":{"themes":["求死","極致的痛苦","渴望"],"sentiment":"VERY_NEGATIVE","keywords":["若要死","愉快","高峯","更多"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[2,4,9,5,3,3,4,2,0,4,3,3,9,3,5,3],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["joek6","jiu3","sei2","ze5","jat1","hak1","zing3","si6","jyu4","faai3","gou1","fung1","cing2","kap1","ngo5","do1"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"若","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"要死","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"這","pos":"DET"},{"text":"一刻","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"正是","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"愉快","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"高峯","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"請","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"給","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"更","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"多","pos":"ADJ"}],"syntax_notes":"在極度痛苦中，反而渴望死亡的來臨，將死亡視為「愉快的高峯」，語氣帶有強烈的求死慾望。"},"source":{"title":"夢到內河","artists":["張國榮"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1093","prev_line_id":"lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0006","next_line_id":"lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0008","paragraph_id":"para_02"}}
{"id":"lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0008","text":"在內河上 我在內河上","structure":{"line_index":8,"char_count":9},"semantics":{"themes":["內心的困境","孤獨"],"sentiment":"NEUTRAL","keywords":["內河","上"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[2,2,0,5,2,2,0],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["zoi6","noi6","ho4","ngo5","zoi6","noi6","ho4"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"在","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"內河","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"上","pos":"PART"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"在","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"內河","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"上","pos":"PART"}],"syntax_notes":"重複「在內河上」，營造一種內心世界的意象，暗示被困於某種狀態，語氣平淡但帶有孤寂感。"},"source":{"title":"夢到內河","artists":["張國榮"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1093","prev_line_id":"lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0007","next_line_id":"lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0009","paragraph_id":"para_03"}}
{"id":"lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0009","text":"望着沿岸高潮 快救活我 溫暖我十秒 快將我怨念傳召","structure":{"line_index":9,"char_count":22},"semantics":{"themes":["求救","渴望","怨念"],"sentiment":"VERY_NEGATIVE","keywords":["望着","高潮","救活","溫暖","怨念","傳召"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[2,2,0,2,3,0,4,4,2,5,3,5,5,2,5,4,3,5,4,2,0,2],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["mong6","zoek6","jyun4","ngon6","gou1","ciu4","faai3","gau3","wut6","ngo5","wan1","nyun5","ngo5","sap6","miu5","faai3","zoeng1","ngo5","jyun3","nim6","cyun4","ziu6"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"望","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"着","pos":"PART"},{"text":"沿岸","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"高潮","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"快","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"救活","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"溫暖","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"十秒","pos":"NUM"},{"text":"快","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"將","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"怨念","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"傳召","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"描繪內心世界的景象，並發出求救的呼喊，渴望被拯救和溫暖，同時也表達了深藏的怨念。"},"source":{"title":"夢到內河","artists":["張國榮"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1093","prev_line_id":"lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0008","next_line_id":"lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0010","paragraph_id":"para_03"}}
{"id":"lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0010","text":"誰還在內河上 猶如做夢那樣 但奈何沒有天橋","structure":{"line_index":10,"char_count":19},"semantics":{"themes":["迷失","現實的隔閡","無助"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["內河","做夢","奈何","天橋"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,0,2,2,0,0,0,2,2,5,2,2,2,0,2,5,3,0],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["seoi4","waan4","zoi6","noi6","ho4","jau4","jyu4","zou6","mung6","naa5","joeng6","daan6","noi6","ho4","mut6","jau5","tin1","kiu4"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"誰","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"還","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"在","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"內河","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"上","pos":"PART"},{"text":"猶如","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"做夢","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"那樣","pos":"PART"},{"text":"但","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"奈何","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"沒有","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"天橋","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"再次回到「內河」的意象，將現實比喻為夢境，並感嘆現實與理想之間無法跨越的鴻溝（天橋），語氣無奈。"},"source":{"title":"夢到內河","artists":["張國榮"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1093","prev_line_id":"lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0009","next_line_id":"lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0011","paragraph_id":"para_03"}}
{"id":"lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0011","text":"跨不過這雙臂膀 會將你壯麗忘掉 如果有這需要","structure":{"line_index":11,"char_count":20},"semantics":{"themes":["隔閡","遺忘","需求"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["跨不過","雙臂膀","壯麗","忘掉","需要"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[4,3,4,5,3,4,9,3,5,4,2,0,2,0,9,5,5,3,4],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["kwaa3","bat1","gwo3","ze5","soeng1","bei3","bong2","zoeng1","nei5","zong3","lai6","mong4","diu6","jyu4","gwo2","jau5","ze5","seoi1","jiu3"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"跨","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"不過","pos":"PART"},{"text":"這","pos":"DET"},{"text":"雙","pos":"NUM"},{"text":"臂膀","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"會","pos":"AUX"},{"text":"將","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"壯麗","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"忘掉","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"如果","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"有","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"這","pos":"DET"},{"text":"需要","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"描述無法跨越的障礙（臂膀），並表達了對對方「壯麗」的遺忘，暗示了關係的疏遠與個人的需求。"},"source":{"title":"夢到內河","artists":["張國榮"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1093","prev_line_id":"lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0010","next_line_id":"lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0012","paragraph_id":"para_03"}}
{"id":"lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0012","text":"差不多不懂感動 就像死掉了 兩腳竟能震動","structure":{"line_index":12,"char_count":18},"semantics":{"themes":["麻木","麻痺","身體的反應"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["不懂","感動","死掉了","兩腳","震動"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[3,3,3,3,9,9,2,2,2,9,2,5,5,4,9,0,4,2],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["caa1","bat1","do1","bat1","dung2","gam2","dung6","zau6","zoeng6","sei2","diu6","liu5","loeng5","goek3","ging2","nang4","zan3","dung6"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"差不多","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"不","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"懂","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"感動","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"就","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"像","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"死","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"掉","pos":"PART"},{"text":"了","pos":"PART"},{"text":"兩腳","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"竟能","pos":"AUX"},{"text":"震動","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"描述情感上的麻木，甚至感覺自己「死掉了」，但身體卻有不自主的反應（震動），形成對比。"},"source":{"title":"夢到內河","artists":["張國榮"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1093","prev_line_id":"lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0011","next_line_id":"lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0013","paragraph_id":"para_04"}}
{"id":"lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0013","text":"不應該這麼激動 仍然能夠哭 我眼睛還有用","structure":{"line_index":13,"char_count":18},"semantics":{"themes":["情感的掙扎","哭泣","自我確認"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["不應該","激動","能夠","哭","眼睛","有用"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[3,3,5,3,3,2,0,0,0,4,3,5,5,3,0,5,2],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["bat1","goi1","ze5","mo1","gik1","dung6","jing4","jin4","nang4","gau3","huk1","ngo5","ngaan5","zing1","waan4","jau5","jung6"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"不","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"應該","pos":"AUX"},{"text":"這麼","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"激動","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"仍然","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"能夠","pos":"AUX"},{"text":"哭","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"眼睛","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"還有","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"用","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"表達不應有的激動，但仍能哭泣，並再次確認「眼睛還有用」，暗示情感的複雜與自我拉扯。"},"source":{"title":"夢到內河","artists":["張國榮"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1093","prev_line_id":"lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0012","next_line_id":"lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0014","paragraph_id":"para_04"}}
{"id":"lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0014","text":"咬住我這雙手吧 但願這陣痛 說我不是發夢","structure":{"line_index":14,"char_count":18},"semantics":{"themes":["痛苦的證明","希望","現實的確認"],"sentiment":"NEUTRAL","keywords":["咬住","雙手","陣痛","不是","發夢"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[5,2,5,5,3,9,2,2,2,5,2,4,4,5,3,2,4,2],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["ngaau5","zyu6","ngo5","ze5","soeng1","sau2","baa6","daan6","jyun6","ze5","zan6","tung3","syut3","ngo5","bat1","si6","faat3","mung6"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"咬住","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"這","pos":"DET"},{"text":"雙手","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"吧","pos":"PART"},{"text":"但願","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"這","pos":"DET"},{"text":"陣痛","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"說","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"不是","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"發夢","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"再次提出極端的請求，希望透過「陣痛」來證明自己不是在做夢，尋求現實的確認。"},"source":{"title":"夢到內河","artists":["張國榮"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1093","prev_line_id":"lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0013","next_line_id":"lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0015","paragraph_id":"para_04"}}
{"id":"lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0015","text":"你爲何這麼衝動 拿流浪的軀體抱擁 直到筋竭力窮","structure":{"line_index":15,"char_count":21},"semantics":{"themes":["衝動","擁抱","疲憊"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["衝動","流浪","軀體","抱擁","筋竭力窮"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[5,0,5,3,3,2,0,0,2,3,3,9,5,9,2,4,3,4,2,0],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["nei5","ho4","ze5","mo1","cung1","dung6","naa4","lau4","long6","dik1","keoi1","tai2","pou5","jung2","zik6","dou3","gan1","kit3","lik6","kung4"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"爲何","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"這麼","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"衝動","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"拿","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"流浪","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"的","pos":"PART"},{"text":"軀體","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"抱擁","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"直到","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"筋","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"竭力","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"窮","pos":"ADJ"}],"syntax_notes":"描述對方衝動的行為，以「流浪的軀體」來擁抱，最終導致雙方都筋疲力盡，語氣帶有疲憊與無奈。"},"source":{"title":"夢到內河","artists":["張國榮"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1093","prev_line_id":"lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0014","next_line_id":"lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0016","paragraph_id":"para_04"}}
{"id":"lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0016","text":"自那日遺下我 我早化做磷火 湖泊上伴你這天鵝","structure":{"line_index":16,"char_count":20},"semantics":{"themes":["被遺棄","轉化","痛苦的陪伴"],"sentiment":"VERY_NEGATIVE","keywords":["遺下","化做","磷火","湖泊","天鵝"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[2,5,2,0,2,5,5,9,4,2,0,9,0,2,2,5,5,3,0],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["zi6","naa5","jat6","wai4","haa6","ngo5","ngo5","zou2","faa3","zou6","leon4","fo2","wu4","bok6","bun6","nei5","ze5","tin1","ngo4"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"自","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"那日","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"遺下","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"早","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"化做","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"磷火","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"湖泊","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"上伴","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"這","pos":"DET"},{"text":"天鵝","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"重複歌詞，再次強調被遺棄後，自身經歷痛苦的轉化，以「磷火」比喻，並在湖泊上「伴」著對方，語氣充滿悲傷與無奈。"},"source":{"title":"夢到內河","artists":["張國榮"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1093","prev_line_id":"lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0015","next_line_id":"lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0017","paragraph_id":"para_05"}}
{"id":"lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0017","text":"但你爲何還要 也許單手 怕扼不死我","structure":{"line_index":17,"char_count":15},"semantics":{"themes":["殘酷的對待","恐懼","求死"],"sentiment":"VERY_NEGATIVE","keywords":["爲何","還要","單手","扼不死"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[2,5,0,0,4,5,9,3,9,4,3,3,9,5],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["daan6","nei5","ho4","waan4","jiu3","jaa5","heoi2","daan1","sau2","paa3","ak1","bat1","sei2","ngo5"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"但","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"爲何","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"還要","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"也許","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"單手","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"怕","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"扼","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"不","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"死","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"}],"syntax_notes":"重複歌詞，再次質疑對方的行為，並表達害怕對方無法徹底傷害自己，語氣帶有恐懼與絕望。"},"source":{"title":"夢到內河","artists":["張國榮"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1093","prev_line_id":"lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0016","next_line_id":"lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0018","paragraph_id":"para_05"}}
{"id":"lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0018","text":"若要死 這一刻正是 愉快 高峯 請給我更多","structure":{"line_index":18,"char_count":17},"semantics":{"themes":["求死","極致的痛苦","渴望"],"sentiment":"VERY_NEGATIVE","keywords":["若要死","愉快","高峯","更多"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[2,4,9,5,3,3,4,2,0,4,3,3,9,3,5,3],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["joek6","jiu3","sei2","ze5","jat1","hak1","zing3","si6","jyu4","faai3","gou1","fung1","cing2","kap1","ngo5","do1"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"若","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"要死","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"這","pos":"DET"},{"text":"一刻","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"正是","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"愉快","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"高峯","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"請","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"給","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"更","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"多","pos":"ADJ"}],"syntax_notes":"重複歌詞，在極度痛苦中，反而渴望死亡的來臨，將死亡視為「愉快的高峯」，語氣帶有強烈的求死慾望。"},"source":{"title":"夢到內河","artists":["張國榮"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1093","prev_line_id":"lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0017","next_line_id":"lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0019","paragraph_id":"para_05"}}
{"id":"lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0019","text":"(誰還)在內河上 我在內河上","structure":{"line_index":19,"char_count":13},"semantics":{"themes":["內心的困境","孤獨","迷失"],"sentiment":"NEUTRAL","keywords":["內河","上"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,0,2,2,0,5,2,2,0],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["seoi4","waan4","zoi6","noi6","ho4","ngo5","zoi6","noi6","ho4"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"(","pos":"PUNCT"},{"text":"誰","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"還","pos":"ADV"},{"text":")","pos":"PUNCT"},{"text":"在","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"內河","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"上","pos":"PART"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"在","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"內河","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"上","pos":"PART"}],"syntax_notes":"括號標示為背景或重複的聲音，再次強調「在內河上」，營造一種內心世界的意象，暗示被困於某種狀態，語氣平淡但帶有孤寂感。"},"source":{"title":"夢到內河","artists":["張國榮"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1093","prev_line_id":"lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0018","next_line_id":"lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0020","paragraph_id":"para_06"}}
{"id":"lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0020","text":"望着沿岸高潮 快救活我 溫暖我十秒 快將我怨念傳召","structure":{"line_index":20,"char_count":22},"semantics":{"themes":["求救","渴望","怨念"],"sentiment":"VERY_NEGATIVE","keywords":["望着","高潮","救活","溫暖","怨念","傳召"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[2,2,0,2,3,0,4,4,2,5,3,5,5,2,5,4,3,5,4,2,0,2],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["mong6","zoek6","jyun4","ngon6","gou1","ciu4","faai3","gau3","wut6","ngo5","wan1","nyun5","ngo5","sap6","miu5","faai3","zoeng1","ngo5","jyun3","nim6","cyun4","ziu6"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"望","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"着","pos":"PART"},{"text":"沿岸","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"高潮","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"快","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"救活","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"溫暖","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"十秒","pos":"NUM"},{"text":"快","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"將","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"怨念","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"傳召","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"重複歌詞，描繪內心世界的景象，並發出求救的呼喊，渴望被拯救和溫暖，同時也表達了深藏的怨念。"},"source":{"title":"夢到內河","artists":["張國榮"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1093","prev_line_id":"lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0019","next_line_id":"lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0021","paragraph_id":"para_06"}}
{"id":"lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0021","text":"誰還在內河上 猶如做夢那樣 但奈何沒有天橋","structure":{"line_index":21,"char_count":19},"semantics":{"themes":["迷失","現實的隔閡","無助"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["內河","做夢","奈何","天橋"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,0,2,2,0,0,0,2,2,5,2,2,2,0,2,5,3,0],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["seoi4","waan4","zoi6","noi6","ho4","jau4","jyu4","zou6","mung6","naa5","joeng6","daan6","noi6","ho4","mut6","jau5","tin1","kiu4"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"誰","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"還","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"在","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"內河","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"上","pos":"PART"},{"text":"猶如","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"做夢","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"那樣","pos":"PART"},{"text":"但","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"奈何","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"沒有","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"天橋","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"重複歌詞，再次回到「內河」的意象，將現實比喻為夢境，並感嘆現實與理想之間無法跨越的鴻溝（天橋），語氣無奈。"},"source":{"title":"夢到內河","artists":["張國榮"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1093","prev_line_id":"lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0020","next_line_id":"lyr_5byg5Zu96I2j_MTA5Mw_0022","paragraph_id":"para_06"}}
